{"tid":1379141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(警世) 試下叫自己勇武，而唔係和理非~","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:59:41.000Z","uid":274336,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"521e8267fd50a406fe21ddb060d335ee153d5b64","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:30.000Z","msg":"6月頭去到今時今日，有一批進化得快的義士變成我們口中的勇武派，佢地令人尊敬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都話勇武成日守係度做乜？又冇目標又唔係衝（唔需要互相指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。其實唔可以否認勇武擋係前線，令到後排人可以安心，甚至有齊full gear的人可以上前，慢慢進化做滅火小隊。其實呢種都係一種練兵的機會。勇武呢幾次比人越拉越多，連儂墻可以拆一貼十，勇武比人拉一個，我地可唔可以鼓勵自己進化多10個勇武出黎?<br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武唔需要分家，大家都係手足，各自分工，齊上齊落，如果大家都可以做到full gear，邊一項工作唔夠人，都可以轉換，咁就係真正的be water啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！呢個係一場革命，大家請唔好營造出自己的comfort zone，唔好框死自己只係勇武或者和理非~大家要一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢我朋友今日下午銅鑼灣做物資幫手，西環要人的時候去左支援，第一次full gear上前線做滅火小隊。<br />\n<br />\n祝福香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c86e8e01437a1e9d2d623a54ec03469c282908d","tid":1379141,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50acb6757929ac9c710ac8df1623c90bc9e7bfec","tid":1379141,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:50:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db887b50b73f782ad20983ead49b264fe9369ee3","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:50:45.000Z","msg":"大家記得自己買裝備啊，幾百蚊完全保護到自己，非常值得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd8e0e36407f3a1b802a2acdaa436df7de36e3b","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"頭盔、眼罩、豬咀，基本配備，唔好省小小錢，救你一命架"},{"pid":"64ef163fa9fb13edd8e752c612ce07a4449bec27","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推，比多d人見到，歡迎討論比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060f64357290064768f3582f9ca20b94d099129f","tid":1379141,"uid":181221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b486b64a7f3a76f3874c9a63e94e49c4ad90c78","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec64b002d5ca8bc4cfd7e33394ba7f2ce3f3dceb","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"full gear啊大家"},{"pid":"960b1c69d35e9d9f3e47b0404500afeb047095ff","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"唔忍再講勇武越嚟越少，要講越嚟越多！"},{"pid":"857a282f5569c0f30a42830d10f2da5694485bb2","tid":1379141,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bad11406f834e789f562724e99a17fd0a0dde7","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:18:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ea09e52be09828da3d6a1c7b10838f14515367","tid":1379141,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":